Package io.dingodb.sdk.annotation

  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    DingoEmbed.EmbedType  
  • Annotation Types Summary 
    Annotation Type Description
    DingoColumn
    Tags a field in a class to be mapped to a Dingo column.
    DingoConstructor
    Tags a constructor to be the one to use when a class as multiple constructors.
    DingoEmbed
    Columns marked with DingoEmbed will have the objects they reference embedded in the parent object, either as a list or a map.
    DingoEnum
    Tags an enum field of a class to set a value field to store its value in the Dingo database instead of the enum constant name.
    DingoExclude
    Columns marked with DingoExclude will not be mapped to the database, irrespective of other annotations.
    DingoGetter
    Tags a field in a class to be mapped to a Dingo column.
    DingoKey  
    DingoOrdinal  
    DingoRecord  
    DingoSetter
    Tags a field in a class to be mapped to a Dingo column.
    FromDingo  
    ParamFrom
    Tags a field in a class to be mapped to an Dingo column.
